title: The 10th Kingdom
description:
At the edge of the mortal world lies a mystical vortex which leads to the Nine Kingdoms, a fantastic land where fairy tales are reinvented....and not with happily-ever-after results!  An evil queen (Wiest) has just doomed Prince Wendell (Lapaine) to life as a dog.  His quest to recapture the throne leads him through a protal to the mythical Tenth Kingdom...Central park!  With the help of ordinary mortals Virginia (Williams) and Tony (Larroquette), they battle evil in a parallel universe of vile trolls. goblins and every fairy tale character imaginable.

Starring: Kimberly Williams, John Larroquette, Diane Wiest, Scott Cohen, Ann-Margaret, Ed O'Neill, Camryn Manheim, Daniel Lapaine, Rutger Hauer, Warwick Davis
